snippet.title: PAYDAY 2: Midland Ranch Heist Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Midland Heist marks the start of the Texas Heat story, Gemma McShay offered to join her in taking down one of her rivals. Said rival has a literal barn of experimental weapons for us to make off with, it should be a blast.

Midland Bundle Store Page - https://pd2.link/MidlandBundleYS
Steam Announcement - https://pd2.link/MidlandRanchYA
